- NC-TODO-FR-001: 01_neocortex_framework/DIR-DOC-FR-001-docs-main/NC-TODO-FR-001-project-roadmap-consolidated.md
- NC-SEC-FR-001:  01_neocortex_framework/DIR-DOC-FR-001-docs-main/NC-SEC-FR-001-atomic-locks.yaml
